Throne of the Dread Terror: Gothmog the Dread Terror -- Tier 1
After the fall of the Witch-king of Angmar, Gothmog has taken control of the hosts of Mordor and Minas Morgul. Arrogant in his connexion to Golodir, he comes to reclaim the throne of Gondor.
You have escaped the fate that Gothmog devised for you
